*Errors in processing queue*

| ID | Priority | Error Type | Context | Queue Position |
|---|---|---|---|---|
`;

        if (this.errorQueue.length === 0) {
            content += '| - | - | - | - | *No queued errors* |\n';
        } else {
            this.errorQueue.forEach((error, index) => {
                const priority = ['CRITICAL', 'HIGH', 'MEDIUM', 'LOW'][error.priority];
                content += `| ${error.id} | ${priority} | ${error.type} | ${error.context} | ${index + 1} |\n`;
            });
        }

        content += `
---

## âœ… RESOLVED ERRORS (Archive)

### ğŸ¯ Successfully Fixed

`;

        if (this.resolvedErrors.size === 0) {
            content += '*No resolved errors yet*\n';
        } else {
            for (const [id, error] of this.resolvedErrors) {
                content += `#### ${id}: ${error.context} âœ…
- **Type:** ${error.type}
- **Context:** ${error.context}
- **First seen:** ${error.firstSeen}
- **Last seen:** ${error.lastSeen}
- **Resolution:** Auto-fixed by error tracker
- **Resolved at:** ${error.resolvedAt}
- **Total attempts:** ${this.fixAttempts.get(id) || 'N/A'}
- **Verification:** âœ… Confirmed working

`;
            }
        }

        content += `---

