### Resolution Metrics
- **Total errors tracked:** ${this.errorIdCounter - 1}
- **Currently active:** ${activeCount}
- **Successfully resolved:** ${resolvedCount}
- **Auto-fix success rate:** ${resolvedCount > 0 ? Math.round((resolvedCount / (resolvedCount + activeCount)) * 100) : 0}%
- **Average attempts per fix:** ${this.calculateAverageAttempts()}

### System Health
